channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: ‘My eyeballs swelled up like golf balls when my eyelash extensions went wrong’
item.description: Beauty treatments are in high demand at the moment, but people are being warned to take care before booking in - as mishandled treatments can have serious health risks

item.title: The mystery of bizarre creature that prowled our oceans 500,000,000 years ago
item.description: It has been nicknamed the 'alien fish taco'.

item.title: Miracle £2 item gets rid of kettle limescale within minutes – and it's not lemon
item.description: Fans of cleaning guru Mrs Hinch have found a cheap and cheerful product that banishes stubborn limescale build-up from your kettle in minutes - and it's not lemon or white vinegar

item.title: Woman who said her husband chained her to tree for 40 days ‘tied herself up’
item.description: The woman initially claimed her husband had left her in the forest for 40 days.

item.title: Meghan Markle's 'odd ritual' after strained reunion with William and Kate
item.description: The royal household was left stunned and blindsided when Prince Harry and Meghan Markle decided to step back from their official duties and relocate to California four years ago

item.title: The 7ft tall dinosaur statue that is so big you can see it on Google Maps
item.description: How many times have you come across a 7ft tall dinosaur while checking out your old street or hometown?

item.title: UK weather: New Met Office maps show thunderstorms to hit while temperatures soar to 33C
item.description: The Met Office has published a map showing thunderstorms hitting parts of the UK after a sweltering weekend, with temperatures expected to hit highs of 33C on Monday

item.title: Meet the man who builds giant versions of household items, because why not?
item.description: Steve Wainwright said his retirement from the ambulance service first prompted him to take on some ‘creative’ building projects.

item.title: Horoscopes today: Daily star sign predictions from Russell Grant on August 11
item.description: Today's horoscope will see one star sign add a little excitement to their life, while another will join forces with a supportive partner. These are your Sunday horoscopes.
